"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我成日都唔開心到個心好痛<br />\n不過的確只係關於另一半既事先會心痛</blockquote><br />\n想當年我同佢同班<br />\n散左之後 日日望住佢同我玩開班朋友<br />\n有講有笑 摸手摸腳咁<br />\n之後我個朋友仲話鍾意左佢<br />\n我每一日個心都好似比刀插緊咁<br />\n去到畢業果日我都係冇勇氣去表白<br />\n係我一生人最後悔嘅事之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而加無心痛咪得<br />\n向前望"},{"pid":"27a68d9916cf52851810ad9168cf1eac9138b32a","tid":236401,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"我都會因為你心痛而心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844998ec97a6ff8d55b12f1bdab62a5147f5ebe6","tid":236401,"uid":47512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:02:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59347936c039ff9833dcdc122a3fc31bb4645503","tid":236401,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係同另一半個時發生<br />\n係好似有人拎把刀 直插入心 再拎返出黎 再插 再拎 再插 再拎<br />\n直到心碎為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你形容得好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}